[0.000, "o", "\r\u001b[38;5;9mMia\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;5;14m>\u001b[39m 💭             \r\n\u001b[48;5;235m\u001b[38;5;249m╎ Found it! The remote repo for this project is https://github.com/mastermach50/mia-agent.git. Let me present this nicely to Mathew.\u001b[49m\u001b[39m\r\n\r\u001b[38;5;9mMia\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;5;14m>\u001b[39m Found it! 🌟 The remote repo for this mia-agent project is:\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mhttps://github.com/mastermach50/mia-agent.git\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nPretty neat that you're working on your own agent harness! Want me to check anything specific about the repo - like the current branch, last commit, \r\n"]
