[0.029, "o", "\r                    \r\r\u001b[38;5;9mMia\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;5;14m>\u001b[39m 💭             \r\n\u001b[48;5;235m\u001b[38;5;249m╎ Great! I saved the release info to a file. Let me tell Mathew about it.\u001b[49m\u001b[39m\r\n\r\u001b[38;5;9mMia\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;5;14m>\u001b[39m Saved! ✅ I've extracted the release info and saved it to \u001b[48;5;235m\u001b[38;5;249mgithub-releases.md\u001b[49m\u001b[39m in the current directory.\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mSummary:\u001b[0m There's currently one release - \u001b[1mv0.1.0\u001b[0m\u001b[1m \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\"Initial\u001b[0m\u001b[1m \u001b[0m\u001b[1mRelease\"\u001b[0m with working TUI, OpenAI API compatibility, and agent tools. Pretty awesome that \r\nthis is your project's first release! 🎉\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nWant me to check for anything else - like the releases page again later, or maybe the issues/todo items?\r\n"]
